{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"64cc399163","title":"对上海市革委会的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"bd8b6875c1","index":0,"year":1967,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"64cc399163","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"军队和军事","id":"6f7a683373","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"e2305b9e63","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"29c7498385","type":"title","text":"对上海市革委会的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"64cc399163","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ffc2102a82","type":"paragraph","text":"对上海市革委会的指示","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"64cc399163","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cbbc820ff2","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"64cc399163","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d8246529bf","type":"paragraph","text":"1967.05.00","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"64cc399163","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"72ac285dc4","type":"paragraph","text":"一、这次双方都有经验，这股风不会刮得很大，我们要遵守“八条”，解放军得遵守“十条”。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"64cc399163","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6438664175","type":"paragraph","text":"二、解放十几年来，我们脱离群众是很厉害的。青联、妇联、团中央都是空架子。我们的要求是不脱产，既当官，又当老百姓。假如不当老百姓，有什么办法呢？一个月里当一个星期的官，三个星期的老百姓。假如不当老百姓，工人运动的领袖，这样下去就可能变。这个是大方向问题。办法是否好，同志们可以提出来。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"64cc399163","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}